  <summary>3/3/1987--Introduced.
Amends title XX (Block Grants to States for Social Services) of the Social Security Act to increase the amount authorized for fiscal years after 1987. Directs States to report annually on the use of such grants over the preceding fiscal year. Requires that certain information regarding the provision of services funded by title XX grants be included in such report.</summary>
